VyGKw43xbmZCBUm1E-ZZuwhZNXu5ePYFtg&oe=66E039F7"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Store Asset Landscape New 2.0.png", "id": "1417069628997019", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974621_1417069635663685_7375261956130428337_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=W4fnVcKZlEkQ7kNvgEcv03r&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAnt0_ISvver9qHighmYmChZzZewmy4Z2IIpeofyXo4-w&oe=66E03C7F"}, "display_name": "Gravity League", "keywords": ["tennis", "racket", "ball", "sport", "fitness"], "long_description": "# Welcome to the future of ball games!\n\nIn a world where gravity is no longer a limitation, the Gravity League has become the ultimate test of skill and endurance for athletes from all corners of the galaxy.\n\n**The rules are simple: 2 players, 1 ball, zero gravity - the first player to 11 goals wins.**\n\n- Compete online with opponents from across the galaxy\n- Play with your friends and compete in custom private matches\n- Explore all our wacky party modes\n- Make your way to the top in the epic Solo Campaign mode\n- Customize your gear with gloves in all shapes and sizes\n- Mix and match gloves to find the best playstyle for you\n- Unlock unique new athletes, balls, gloves, and stadiums\n- Team up with your friends for a 2v2 action\n\n\n**So strap on your Gravity Gloves and get ready to take on the competition!**", "short_description": "Welcome to the future of ball games! \n\nIn a world where gravity is no longer a limitation, the Gravity League has become the ultimate test of skill and endurance for athletes from all corners of the galaxy.\n\nThe rules are simple: 2 players, 1 ball, zero gravity - the first player to get 11 goals wins.\n\nSo strap on your Gravity Gloves and get ready to take on the competition!\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://blue-duck-studios.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Blue Duck Studios Ltd.", 